Deafbox Industries.title: The Rise and Fall of
Deafbox Industries.label: Deafbox Industries
Deafbox Industries.about:
Basic Bitches = Wolves in Sheepskin + The Beatloads
Recorded on two separate days in 2016, the combination of these two bands resulted in some incredibly intense and dynamic music. The earth quaked. There was shouting. Tears of joy and frustration were shed. It was a calamity. It was some of the greatest times of our lives.
Deafbox Industries.credits:
released June 30, 2017
Personnel:
Christophe Bassett
Stryder Rymber
